solution_code: public class Solution {--newline--    public int findMin(int[] nums) {--newline--         int l = 0, r = nums.length-1;--newline--         while (l < r) {--newline--             int mid = (l + r) / 2;--newline--             if (nums[mid] < nums[r]) {--newline--                 r = mid;--newline--             } else if (nums[mid] > nums[r]){--newline--                 l = mid + 1;--newline--             } else {  --newline--                 r--;  //nums[mid]=nums[r] no idea, but we can eliminate nums[r];--newline--             }--newline--         }--newline--         return nums[l];--newline--    }--newline--}
